            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>clotted cream </strong>and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Tip: Add more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p><p>Squeeze in the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>chorizo & lemon linguine</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
